{"book": 24, "chapter": 18, "sections": [{"type": "heading", "heading": "耶利米在陶匠的家"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華的話臨到耶利米說： "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "「你起來，下到窰匠的家裏去，我在那裏要使你聽我的話。」 "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我就下到窰匠的家裏去，正遇他轉輪做器皿。 "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "窰匠用泥做的器皿，在他手中做壞了，他又用這泥另做別的器皿；窰匠看怎樣好，就怎樣做。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華的話就臨到我說： "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "「耶和華說：以色列家啊，我待你們，豈不能照這窰匠弄泥嗎？以色列家啊，泥在窰匠的手中怎樣，你們在我的手中也怎樣。 "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我何時論到一邦或一國說，要拔出、拆毀、毀壞； "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我所說的那一邦，若是轉意離開他們的惡，我就必後悔，不將我想要施行的災禍降與他們。 "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我何時論到一邦或一國說，要建立、栽植； "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們若行我眼中看為惡的事，不聽從我的話，我就必後悔，不將我所說的福氣賜給他們。 "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "現在你要對猶大人和耶路撒冷的居民說：『耶和華如此說：我造出災禍攻擊你們，定意刑罰你們。你們各人當回頭離開所行的惡道，改正你們的行動作為。』"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "「他們卻說：『這是枉然。我們要照自己的計謀去行。』各人隨自己頑梗的惡心做事。」"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "百姓忘記耶和華"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "所以，耶和華如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們且往各國訪問，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "有誰聽見這樣的事？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 以色列民行了一件極可憎惡的事。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 黎巴嫩的雪從田野的磐石上豈能斷絕呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "從遠處流下的涼水豈能乾涸呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我的百姓竟忘記我，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "向假神燒香，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使他們在所行的路上，在古道上絆跌，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使他們行沒有修築的斜路，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "以致他們的地令人驚駭，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "常常嗤笑；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "凡經過這地的必驚駭搖頭。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我必在仇敵面前分散他們，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "好像用東風吹散一樣。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "遭難的日子，我必以背向他們，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不以面向他們。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "謀害耶利米"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們就說：「來吧！我們可以設計謀害耶利米；因為我們有祭司講律法，智慧人設謀略，先知說預言，都不能斷絕。來吧！我們可以用舌頭擊打他，不要理會他的一切話。」"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華啊，求你理會我，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "且聽那些與我爭競之人的話。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "豈可以惡報善呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們竟挖坑要害我的性命！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "求你記念我怎樣站在你面前為他們代求，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要使你的忿怒向他們轉消。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "故此，願你將他們的兒女交與饑荒和刀劍；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "願他們的妻無子，且作寡婦；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "又願他們的男人被死亡所滅，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的少年人在陣上被刀擊殺。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你使敵軍忽然臨到他們的時候，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "願人聽見哀聲從他們的屋內發出；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因他們挖坑要捉拿我，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "暗設網羅要絆我的腳。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華啊，他們要殺我的那一切計謀，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你都知道。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不要赦免他們的罪孽，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "也不要從你面前塗抹他們的罪惡，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要叫他們在你面前跌倒；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "願你發怒的時候罰辦他們。"}]}]}